text: int main ( ) { int t , i , a , b , j ; scanf ( "%d" , & t ) ; for ( i = 0 ; i < t ; i ++ ) { scanf ( "%d %d" , & a , & b ) ; int gcd , lcm ; for ( j = 1 ; j <= a && j <= b ; j ++ ) { if ( a % j == 0 && b % j == 0 ) { gcd = j ; } } lcm = ( a * b ) / gcd ; printf ( "%d %d\n" , gcd , lcm ) ; } return 0 ; }
